title: Introduction to C Programming
description: Get started with C programming. Learn about variables, control structures, and functions. This course provides a solid foundation in C.

title: Introduction to Algorithms
description: Master algorithms, including sorting and searching. Enhance your problem-solving skills and algorithmic thinking.

title: Introduction to C++ for DSA
description: Advance your C++ skills with a focus on data structures and algorithms. Covers OOP and key concepts.

title: Basic Data Structures
description: Explore essential data structures: arrays, linked lists, stacks, and queues. Gain proficiency in their use.

title: Introduction to OOP Python
description: Learn Python OOP principles - classes, inheritance, and polymorphism. Create modular, maintainable code.

title: Software Engineering
description: Study software engineering methodologies and project management. Develop skills for software design.

title: AWS, Cloud Computing
description: Gain hands-on experience with AWS. Learn to deploy and manage services like EC2, S3, and Lambda.

title: Database (MySQL)
description: Master MySQL - design, query, and administer databases. Acquire expertise in effective database management.

title: Problem-Solving Part
description: Enhance problem-solving skills for coding interviews and competitive programming. Learn techniques and algorithmic thinking.
